OL,3,CMan who caught migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cstill in limbo over huge Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FA Gloucestershire man who was issued a
OL,8,F#12,000 fine after alerting the
OL,9,Fauthorities to stowaways in his lorry
OL,10,Fwhen he was coming back from France is
OL,11,Fstill "in limbo" over the charge.
OL,13,FMichael Fletcher, 63, from the Forest
OL,14,Fof Dean spoke out in October this year
OL,15,Fand said he was facing debt collectors
OL,16,Fand was being penalised by Border
OL,17,FForce "for doing the right thing."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
