OL,3,CMan who caught migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cstill in limbo over huge Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FMr Fletcher, who has worked in
OL,8,Ftransportation since he passed his
OL,9,Fdriving test in the late 1970s, was
OL,10,Fabout to board the ferry at Calais on
OL,11,FSaturday 16 September last year when
OL,12,Fhe felt his vehicle move.
OL,14,FHe alerted border guards of his
OL,15,Fsuspicions and after a check, they
OL,16,Ffound two stowaways in the back of his
OL,17,Fvehicle.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
