OL,3,CMan who caught migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cstill in limbo over huge Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FMr Fletcher said officers advised him
OL,8,Fthat he had done all the necessary
OL,9,Fchecks, so he was shocked to receive a
OL,10,Fletter from Border Force in February
OL,11,Fdemanding payment of #12,000.
OL,13,FDriver forced to change his job and
OL,14,Fonly work within the UK
OL,16,FThey claimed in the letter that Mr
OL,17,FFletcher couldn't produce a checklist
OL,18,Fat the time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
