OL,3,CMan who caught migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cstill in limbo over huge Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FAfter disputing this, and providing a
OL,8,Fphotograph which shows his checklist,
OL,9,FBorder Force is now seeking payment
OL,10,Ffor a reduced fine of #3,000.
OL,12,FMr Fletcher said he is wrongly being
OL,13,Ftargeted for doing the right thing and
OL,14,Fdoes not see why he should pay for not
OL,15,Fdoing anything wrong.
OL,17,FHe believes he has been sent the fine
OL,18,Fbecause border guards did not do their
OL,19,Fwork correctly.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
