OL,3,CMan who caught migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cstill in limbo over huge Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FHe said he is stressed by the
OL,8,Fsituation, and has changed his job in
OL,9,Fthe meantime so that he only works in
OL,10,Ftransportation within the UK.
OL,12,FMr Fletcher raised the issue with his
OL,13,Fcounty councillor Philip Robinson
OL,14,F(Con, Mitcheldean) earlier this year
OL,15,Fwho suggested he speak with his then
OL,16,FMP, Mark Harper.
OL,18,FThe previous Conservative MP raised
OL,19,Fthe issue with then Home Secretary
OL,20,FJames Cleverly who was in the process
OL,21,Fof looking into the issue.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
