OL,3,CMan who caught migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cstill in limbo over huge Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FThis stalled after Parliament was
OL,8,Fdissolved and Mr Harper lost his seat,
OL,9,Fso is no longer dealing with his case.
OL,10,FHe said he has since been unable to
OL,11,Fget the new Forest of Dean MP Matt
OL,12,FBishop to solve his case.
OL,14,FMr Fletcher said he still doesn't know
OL,15,Fwhat's going to happen with the fine,
OL,16,Fand he feels like he is "in limbo."
OL,18,F'I want them to take the mark off my
OL,19,Fpassport' - Michael Fletcher
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
