OL,3,CMan who caught migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cstill in limbo over huge Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FHe said he needs the issue to be
OL,8,Fresolved so that he can continue
OL,9,Fworking in Europe.
OL,11,FHe said: "Nobody's said anything and I
OL,12,Fthink they want it to go quiet so
OL,13,Fnobody knows and then come back at me
OL,14,Flater. Normally, if they had a
OL,15,Fcollection person to collect stuff,
OL,16,Fthey would have been by now.
OL,18,F"They did tell me in Newport that they
OL,19,Fhad handed it to a debt collection
OL,20,Fcompany before I spoke out about it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
