OL,3,CMan who caught migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cstill in limbo over huge Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,F"If it does get wiped off, I want them
OL,8,Fto take the mark off my passport and
OL,9,Fat least give me an apology for
OL,10,Fmessing me about."
OL,12,FCouncillor Robinson said he thought Mr
OL,13,FFletcher's issue was going to be
OL,14,Fresolved quickly.
OL,16,F"I am really disappointed the MP has
OL,17,Fstill not taken a personal interest in
OL,18,Ftrying to resolve it," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
