OL,3,CMan who caught migrants in his lorry
OL,4,Cstill in limbo over huge Border Force
OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,F"I had thought it was about to be
OL,8,Fresolved but low and behold nothing
OL,9,Fhas happened. He continues to be the
OL,10,Finvisible MP."
OL,12,FMr Bishop said his office has
OL,13,Fcontacted Mr Fletcher many times and
OL,14,Fhas written to the Home Office for an
OL,15,Fupdate.
OL,17,FThe Labour MP also said Cllr Robinson
OL,18,Fhas not engaged with him and his
OL,19,Foffice about the matter at all.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
