OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FMr Bishop said: "My office has
OL,8,Fcontacted Mr Fletcher many times to
OL,9,Fdiscuss this case. I have also written
OL,10,Fto the Home Office for an update, and
OL,11,Fthis has been communicated to Mr
OL,12,FFletcher. Cllr Robinson has not
OL,13,Fengaged with me or my office about
OL,14,Fthis matter at all," he said.
OL,16,F"If he would like to hear about what I
OL,17,Fhave been working on since being
OL,18,Felected, I would welcome a
OL,19,Fconversation with him."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
