OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FThe law changed in 2023 during the
OL,8,Fprevious Conservative Government and
OL,9,Fincreased fines, new maximum penalty
OL,10,Flevels and a new penalty for failing
OL,11,Fto adequately secure a goods vehicle
OL,12,Fcame into force to prevent dangerous
OL,13,Fand illegal journeys to the UK.
OL,15,FThe Clandestine Entrant Civil Penalty
OL,16,FScheme is designed to target
OL,17,Fnegligence rather than criminality.
OL,18,FDrivers who are actively involved in
OL,19,Fpeople smuggling will still be
OL,20,Finvestigated and prosecuted in the
OL,21,Fcourts.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
