OL,5,Cfine
OL,7,FResponsible persons who have complied
OL,8,Fwith the actions laid out in the
OL,9,FCarriers Liability Amendment
OL,10,FRegulation 2023 are eligible for a
OL,11,Fdiscount on their penalty.
OL,13,FA Home Office spokesperson previously
OL,14,Fsaid: "We are fully committed to
OL,15,Fsecuring the border and cracking down
OL,16,Fon people smugglers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
