OL,7,F"The Clandestine Entrant Civil Penalty
OL,8,FScheme aims to ensure drivers are
OL,9,Ftaking every reasonable step to deter
OL,10,Firregular migration and disrupt people
OL,11,Fsmugglers."
OL,13,FThe Home Office has been contacted for
OL,14,Ffurther comment.
